<td style="text-align: left; vertical-align: top;"><span style="font-size: 20px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;">Honeywell to feature Avionics, Propulsion and Connectivity Products at HELI-EXPO 2016</span><br /><span style="font-size: 12px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;"> From March 1-3, helicopter suppliers and airframe manufacturers will participate in the world&rsquo;s largest trade show dedicated to the international helicopter community. The HELI-EXPO Trade Show and Exhibition in Louisville, KY will draw more than 20,000 attendees from 80 countries.</span><br /> <br /><span style="font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 12px;"> <a href="https://aerospace.honeywell.com/news-listing/2016/february/honeywell-to-feature-avionics-propulsion-and-connectivity-products-at-heli-expo-2016">Continue Reading&nbsp;</a>&nbsp;</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><br /> <br /></td>
