<td style="text-align: left; vertical-align: top;"><span style="font-size: 20px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;">Heli-Expo Presentations to Feature Honeywell Turboshaft Engines</span><br /><span style="font-size: 12px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;"> Light helicopter operators and aircraft and powerplant technicians working on Honeywell&rsquo;s proven T53 and LTS101 turboshaft engines will want to spend some time with us at this year&rsquo;s Heli-Expo in Louisville.</span><br /> <br /><span style="font-size: 12px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;"> <a href="https://aerospace.honeywell.com/news-listing/2016/february/heli-expo-presentations-to-feature-honeywell-turboshaft-engines">Continue Reading</a></span><br /> <br /></td>
