<td style="text-align: left; vertical-align: top;"><span style="font-size: 20px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;">Laseref VI Delivers Peak Performance for Twin Helos</span><br /><span style="font-size: 12px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;"> Now, more than ever, helicopter operators need a navigation system they can count on &ndash; one that works even when GPS signals are not available. Honeywell&rsquo;s proven Laseref inertial navigation technology has been helping pilots stay on course for decades.</span><br /> <br /><span style="font-size: 12px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;"> <a href="https://aerospace.honeywell.com/news-listing/2016/february/laseref-vi-delivers-peak-performance-for-twin-helos">Continue Reading</a>&nbsp;</span><br /> <br /></td>
