<td style="text-align: left; vertical-align: top;"><span style="font-size: 20px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;">Honeywell, Mecaer Aviation Group (MAG) Improve Service for Northeast Customers</span><br /><span style="font-size: 12px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;"> A new collaboration between Honeywell and MAG, Inc. (MAG) is providing better access to avionics repair and overhaul services for commercial helicopter operators in the northeastern United States.</span><br /> <br /><span style="font-size: 12px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;"> <a href="https://aerospace.honeywell.com/news-listing/2016/february/honeywell-mecaer-aviation-group-improve-service-for-northeast-customers">Continue Reading</a>&nbsp;</span><br /> <br /></td>
