<td style="text-align: left; vertical-align: top;"><span style="font-size: 20px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;">The Secret to HAPPiness</span><br /><span style="font-size: 12px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;"> Honeywell Avionics Protection Plan (HAPP) is a unique service plan in that it places a priority on the customers&rsquo; needs. The 24/7 customer support and globally located SPEX warehouses create an environment of constant contact and efficient processes. </span><br /> <br /><span style="font-size: 12px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;"> <a href="https://aerospace.honeywell.com/blogs/2016/january/the-secret-to-happiness">Continue Reading</a>&nbsp;</span><br /> <br /></td>
