<div style="color: #000000; font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 11px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;"><span style="font-size: 20px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;">Product Spotlight</span></div>
<div style="color: #000000; font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 11px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;"><span style="font-size: 12px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;">Vocollect voice solutions help optimize workflow processes increasing worker productivity up to 35%, while reducing errors up to 25%, and training time up to 50%. We provide the top-performing voice recognition technology platform purpose-built for challenging industrial environments and our elegant, integrated total solution design, from the headset to host data system integration, results in maximum worker confidence and ergonomics.</span></div>
<p><span style="font-size: 12px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;">The system is designed specifically for the challenging industrial environment by utilizing the world&rsquo;s most accurate speech recognition software solution. Our Vocollect Blue Streak recognition engine is the number one influencer in helping you save 30% or more in MRO / analytical time.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 107%; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;"><a href="http://www.vocollectvoice.com/">Learn more&gt;</a></span></p>
